.PP
Notes
.IP \(bu 2
\fBsq\fR operates against an IaC root directory (defaults to CWD when not provided).
.IP \(bu 2
When using encrypted state, \fBsq\fR will prompt for a passphrase or use \fBTF_VAR_passphrase\fR\&.

